  "descriptions": {
    "en": {
      "language": "en",
      "value": "[松平忠雅] daimyo of the mid Edo period (1683-1746); lord of Yamagara, Fukuyama then Kuwana"
    },
    "ja": {
      "language": "ja",
      "value": "江戸時代前期から中期の大名。出羽山形・備後福山を経て伊勢桑名藩初代藩主。奥平松平家3代。"
    }
